European Central Bank Said to Be Purchasing Italian Bonds Today

-- B y   K e i t h   J e n k i n s   a n d   G a b i   T h e s i n g
-- 
2011-09-20T08:36:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/european-central-bank-said-to-be-purchasing-italian-bonds-today.html
The  European Central Bank  bought
Italian government bonds today, according to three people with
knowledge of the transactions, who asked not to be identified
because the deals are confidential.   A spokeswoman for the central bank declined to comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Keith Jenkins in London at 
